productname: Amazon Ethernet Adapter for Amazon Fire TV Devices
reviews: This is my third of these. Getting FireTV to Ethernet really improves everything.

productname: Amazon Ethernet Adapter for Amazon Fire TV Devices
reviews: It works, but is a clunky product that adds to the cable mess. I'd much rather a fire stick model with integrated Ethernet port, even if it cost the same as these two (stick+adapter) combined. Laptop USB to Ethernet adapter is tiny, why does this need to be large with an extra short cable?Works so 4 stars.

productname: Amazon Ethernet Adapter for Amazon Fire TV Devices
reviews: Very good

productname: Amazon Ethernet Adapter for Amazon Fire TV Devices
reviews: Tem arrived quickly. Easy to setup and improves data speed.

productname: Amazon Ethernet Adapter for Amazon Fire TV Devices
reviews: I have 1000mbps down and this limits my Firestick to about 90 mbps. I get about 150mbps using wifi6 (because vpn) and after extensive testing, Wifi is faster and i ended up removing it. However, it does work. Just not what I needed.

productname: Amazon Ethernet Adapter for Amazon Fire TV Devices
reviews: A must for simple and secure.A must for speed.Remote works even better with this

productname: Amazon Ethernet Adapter for Amazon Fire TV Devices
reviews: Saves plugging in power point no need for cables very good thanks

productname: Amazon Ethernet Adapter for Amazon Fire TV Devices
reviews: Needs a 5 year warranty, didn't last as long as my firetv... is just a generic cat5 to usb connector...wont be getting another, wifi is decent at our house so we have no issue with that so this is waste of money and fails after only two years.

productname: Amazon Ethernet Adapter for Amazon Fire TV Devices
reviews: Does what it supposed to, keeps streaming speeds constant

productname: Amazon Ethernet Adapter for Amazon Fire TV Devices
reviews: Not enough oomph for Disney and Netflix 4k, 100 mps to slow, both above need the 1 gig ethernet
